"  8 bone-in, skinless chicken thighs (about 2 pounds)","  3/4 teaspoon kosher salt","  1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","  1 tablespoon grated lemon rind","  4 teaspoons olive oil","  4 cups thinly sliced leek (about 3 large)","  3 tablespoons fresh lemon juice","  2 teaspoons honey","  2 tablespoons chopped fresh parsley or chives (optional)","  Lemon wedges (optional)"